http://www.foobar2000.org/

////////////////////////////// Introduction /////////////////////////////////
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

This Foobar2000 plug-in is a part of the TTA audio compressor which performs
lossless compression on multichannel wav audio files. Being "lossless" means
that no data/quality is lost in the compression - when uncompressed, the data
will be identical to the original. This plugin supports up to 8 channels TTA
files, with audio resolution 16 or 24 bits per sample. TTA format supports of
ID3v1/v2 and APEv2 tags. Detailed format description is available at
http://www.true-audio.com

////////////////////////////// Configuration ////////////////////////////////
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

1. Copy the file foo_input_tta.dll out of your Foobar2000
   components directory (usually C:\Program Files\foobar2000\components).
2. Start Foobar2000.
3. Play TTA files and enjoy highest quality sound.

* Requirements

Nice sound card and good speakers.

